  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast, tuck into a tasty buffet with cooked and continental options. For dinner you can enjoy a delicious meal that is either a lovely buffet or a three-course dinner (dinner serving style is dependent on the number of guests in house). </p>
<p>If you wish, you can choose to upgrade your dinner to four-courses at a supplement (bookable and payable locally, approx. NOK 205 per person, per dinner).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
